text: MYSA or variants may refer to: * Mathare Youth Sports Association, in Nairobi, Kenya * MySA, a web site of the San Antonio Express-News in San Antonio, Texas * Malaysian Space Agency, the national space agency of Malaysia * Mysa Nal, the name of the White Witch, a fictional comic book character in the DC Universe * Mysa, a water buffalo character in The Jungle Book by Rudyard Kipling
title: MYSA
